<%= render "marketing_nav" %>

<section class="relative overflow-hidden landing-hero-drench pt-24 pb-20" data-controller="reveal">
  <div class="landing-hero-pattern"></div>
  <div class="landing-blob landing-blob-1"></div>
  <div class="landing-blob landing-blob-2"></div>
  <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 pt-16">
    <div class="grid items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-medium tracking-widest text-[#b8d4b5] uppercase mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-mono);">For Loan Officers</p>
        <h1 class="landing-hero-title text-balance text-5xl leading-none sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">
          Process loans<br>
          <span class="landing-hero-accent">in hours, not weeks.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="landing-hero-body mt-6 max-w-xl text-balance text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Application, documents, credit evaluation, approval, disbursement — all on one platform.
          No chasing paper across desks. No spreadsheet amortizations. Your loan officers spend
          time evaluating credit, not filling out forms.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
          <a href="#demo" class="landing-hero-cta landing-hero-cta-primary">See It in Action</a>
          <a href="/session/new" class="landing-hero-cta landing-hero-cta-outline">Try a Demo</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hidden lg:block">
        <div class="landing-browser-frame">
          <div class="landing-browser-toolbar">
            <span class="landing-browser-dot" style="background:#ff5f57"></span>
            <span class="landing-browser-dot" style="background:#ffbd2e"></span>
            <span class="landing-browser-dot" style="background:#28c840"></span>
          </div>
          <img src="<%= image_path('screenshots/dashboard.svg') %>" alt="Loan officer dashboard in Sirib">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-[#f0f7ef] border-b border-[#e7e5e4] py-12" data-controller="reveal">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="landing-stats-value">50+</p>
        <p class="landing-stats-label">applications processed per day</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="landing-stats-value">4 hrs</p>
        <p class="landing-stats-label">average processing time per loan</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="landing-stats-value">98%</p>
        <p class="landing-stats-label">documentation completeness rate</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="border-b border-[#e7e5e4] py-24 bg-white relative overflow-hidden" data-controller="reveal">
  <div class="landing-blob landing-blob-3" style="top: -5rem; right: 15%; opacity: 0.6;"></div>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <p class="text-xs font-medium tracking-widest text-[#5b8c5a] uppercase mb-3" style="font-family: var(--font-mono);">The Flow</p>
      <h2 class="text-balance text-3xl font-normal tracking-[-0.03em] text-[#1c1917] sm:text-4xl">
        What a loan application looks like in Sirib
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-4" data-reveal-item>
      <div class="text-center relative">
        <div class="mx-auto w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-[#f0f7ef] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-[#5b8c5a]">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M9 12h6M9 12a2 2 0 1 0 0 4h6a2 2 0 1 0 0-4M9 12v4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs font-medium text-[#3d6b3c] mb-2" style="font-family: var(--font-mono); letter-spacing: 0.1em;">STEP 1</p>
        <h3 class="text-base font-medium text-[#1c1917] mb-2">Application received</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6e6358]">Loan application submitted and logged. Member history — savings, previous loans, standing — all on one screen for the officer to review.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center relative">
        <div class="mx-auto w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-[#f0f7ef] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-[#5b8c5a]">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v12a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h10a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-2"/><path d="M9 5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v0a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs font-medium text-[#3d6b3c] mb-2" style="font-family: var(--font-mono); letter-spacing: 0.1em;">STEP 2</p>
        <h3 class="text-base font-medium text-[#1c1917] mb-2">Documents collected</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6e6358]">Requirements checklist tracked digitally. System flags what's missing. No chasing paperwork across desks — everything uploaded and linked to the application.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center relative">
        <div class="mx-auto w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-[#f0f7ef] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-[#5b8c5a]">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M9 7a2 2 0 1 1 4 0v4a2 2 0 0 1-4 0V7z"/><path d="M3 12a9 9 0 1 0 18 0 9 9 0 0 0-18 0"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs font-medium text-[#3d6b3c] mb-2" style="font-family: var(--font-mono); letter-spacing: 0.1em;">STEP 3</p>
        <h3 class="text-base font-medium text-[#1c1917] mb-2">Credit evaluation</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6e6358]">Automated debt-to-income ratio, amortization schedule, and capacity analysis. Officer reviews the numbers and renders a decision — not build the spreadsheet.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center relative">
        <div class="mx-auto w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-[#f0f7ef] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-[#5b8c5a]">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs font-medium text-[#3d6b3c] mb-2" style="font-family: var(--font-mono); letter-spacing: 0.1em;">STEP 4</p>
        <h3 class="text-base font-medium text-[#1c1917] mb-2">Approval + disbursement</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6e6358]">Loan approved, terms set, amortization schedule generated. Disbursement releases funds and sets up the repayment schedule — one action, everything updates.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

