        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6e6358]">Automated reminders for due dates. Configured per loan product. Officers spend less time on collection follow-up and more time on new applications.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-[#e7e5e4] p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#f0f7ef] flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-[#5b8c5a]">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M9 17v-2m3 2v-4m3 4v-6m2 10H7a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h5.586a1 1 0 0 1 .707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 0 1 .293.707V19a2 2 0 0 1-2 2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-[#1c1917]">Covenant tracking</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6e6358]">Late payments, breaches, and maturing loans flagged automatically. Officers get a dashboard view of their entire portfolio status — not just the applications in front of them.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

